oldUnderline">facilitate</span><span style="font-size: 6pt;">¶ </span><span class="StyleBoldUnderline">food imports through market opening measures, or some combination of the two</span><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> strategies. As the examples</span><span style="font-size: 6pt;">¶</span><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> in this report demonstrate, major efforts are underway to expand and enhance transportation infrastructure</span><span style="font-size: 6pt;">¶</span><span style="font-size: 8pt;"> in the region.</span>

